Promote a user-level lens (or draft) to org-level so all teammates see it. Admin-only.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} rare — when an admin user has built a lens (or refined a draft) and wants to share it org-wide.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} as a non-admin (will fail with 403); for personal lens changes (those stay user-scoped).

{{include:headers/verification-required-if-write}}
